            "reviews": "“Even better than its predecessor”<br>9.5/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.godisageek.com/reviews/the-banner-saga-2-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >God is a Geek</a><br><br>“As beautiful and tactical as the first, but with greater variety in combat and story.”<br>8.9/10 – <a href=\"http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/04/19/the-banner-saga-2-review\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >IGN</a><br><br>“A gorgeous, challenging strategy game that's starting to tell one hell of a story.”<br><a href=\"http://kotaku.com/the-banner-saga-2-the-kotaku-review-1771538819\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Kotaku</a><br>",
